<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>LOQUO iOS App</title>

    <!-- Link to the CSS file -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/loquo.css">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Back button -->
    <div class="back-button-container">
        <button onclick="goBack()" class="back-btn">
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Go Back
        </button>
    </div>

    <script>
        function goBack() {
            window.history.back(); // Go back to the previous page
        }
    </script>
    
    <div class="image-container">
        <img src="/images/loquo-logo.png" alt="LOQUO Logo">
        <div class="button-container">
            <a href="/downloads/LOQUO-TFG-JoseLuisEscolá.pdf" class="download-btn" download>Download LOQUO Documentation PDF</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Key elements of the app -->
    <div class="key-elements-container">
        <h2>Key elements include:</h2>
        <ul class="key-elements-list">
            <li>API/Server connection for data management.</li>
            <li>Use of CoreData for managing local data, synced with a central database.</li>
            <li>Creation of user interfaces and features for PUSH notifications, user management, and chat.</li>
            <li>Development based on agile methodologies like SCRUM and Kanban, ensuring efficient teamwork and iterative improvement.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</body>
</html>